<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA64">
<l>kataiyiṉ perumporuḷuṅ kaṇṇāniṉ pērē</l>
<l>yitaiya miruntavaiyē yēttiṟ – kataiyun</l>
<l>tirumoḻiyāy niṉṟa tirumālē yuṉṉaip</l>
<l>parumoḻiyāṟ kāṇap paṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great meaning of the stories, Kaṇṇaṉ, is but your name,</l>
<l>if one praises in one’s heart what has happened. O Tirumāl</l>
<l>who stands as the sacred word of all stories, humbly</l>
<l>show yourself by great words.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
